  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">is confident that he will receive help from him. Now it has been stated above ( Article 1, Reply to Objection 2 ) that magnanimity is chiefly about the hope of something difficult. Wherefore, since confidence denotes a certain strength of hope arising from some observation which gives one</data>
