  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As stated above ( II-II:129:3 ad 1 ), magnanimity observes the means, not as regards the quantity of that to which it tends, but in proportion to our own ability: for it does not tend to anything greater than</data>
  <data key="d18">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d19">honor_worthiness</data>
</edge>
<edge source="st.ii-ii.q130.a002" target="concept.presumption_magnanimity" id="edge.st.ii-ii.q130.a002.treated_in.concept.presumption_magnanimity">
